businesses.name: Staysafe Industry Training
businesses.business_details:
Louise Vause is a former QLD Government quality assurance Auditor whose role it was to audit QLD RTO's against the AQTF Standards. My goal was to start an RTO which became a reality in June 2014. 
This is a very rewarding industry and I love being involved as a trainer and assessor for some courses that we offer.
businesses.product_details: Staysafe is across a diversity of industries such as QLD White card, QBCC Managerial course, Playground safety inspector training, Working at heights, Grid connect PV systems design and install, among other courses.
businesses.headline: Get connected and training online and video streaming/remote learning
